# ─── Node ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/

# ─── Build output ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# frontend/dist/ is now INTENTIONALLY TRACKED, not ignored.
# GitHub Actions (.github/workflows/prerender-deploy.yml) builds + prerenders
# it with react-snap and commits it to main. Hostinger's auto-deploy then
# just serves the committed dist — see scripts/build-frontend.js.

